<br>
1) Loves doing the most damage over time. Given the restrictions on big nukes, they typically are Draught fans. In their world, SoS is fun, but nothing to get too excited about.<br>
<br>
2) Loves giant crits. To them, SoS is the holy grail, since Shock of Magic is too random for them to count on insane 9k crits like they dream of.<br>
<br>
Someone who said SoS sucks was likely someone in the first camp having a bad day. <p><a href="http://eq.guildmagic.com/character.cfm?ID=49189" target="_blank"><img src="http://www.lby3.com/eq/whiz/whiz_toon.gif" height="104" width="390" alt="stats" border=0></a>
