<br>
When grinding, sure, you want the smaller nukes.  But let's not forget about the fun factor here.  I like the comments I get from friends when I dish out huge crits.<br>
<br>
Use the smaller nukes to gain in power so you can use better large nuke crits to impress your friends more and more.  Regardless of efficiency, the large crits will improve your faction with most groups.<br>
<br>
-Raystonn<br>
